    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid seepage and a suspension that feels a bit loose on rougher roads. The exterior has several visible scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood, while the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery and a few cracked trim pieces. It is a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable entry into this model who doesn't mind performing some cosmetic and mechanical TLC over time.",
