      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist's specification featuring the S54B32 inline-six, renowned for its 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring mechanical grip and driver engagement. It has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to maintain optimal cam timing. The chassis is tightened with updated bushings and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced. Offering a visceral, naturally aspirated power band and hydraulic steering feedback, this example represents a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car ready for the apex.",
